   :author: bmiller
   :difficulty: 3
   :basecourse: authorguide
   :topic: directives/parsons
   :from_source: T
   :language: c++

   Construct a block of code that correctly implements the accumulator pattern.
   -----
   template&lt;class InputIt, class T&gt;
   =====
   T sum(InputIt first, InputIt last, T value)
   {
   =====
       while (first != last) {
   =====
          value = value + *first;
   =====
          ++first;
   =====
       }
       return value;
   =====
   }